value.title: VP Mike Pence, in Ohio, criticizes removal of statues in Columbus, elsewhere
value.excerpt: Vice President Mike Pence, campaigning in Ohio on Monday, suggested that America is on the edge of a cultural precipice, denouncing the removal of statues of controversial explorer Christopher Columbus in his namesake city and around the country.

value.title: Jill Biden to campaign in Texas as Dems look to flip Lone Star State
value.excerpt: Democratic presidential nominee Joe Biden hasn't traveled to Texas in months, but on Tuesday, his campaign will dispatch his wife, Jill Biden, to help boost early voting turnout.

value.title: Columbus Day: Trump accuses 'radical activists' of trying to undermine explorer's legacy in holiday proclamation

value.title: Ex-Ohio State QB Cardale Jones says Pence rally appearance had 'no political or social attachment'
value.excerpt: In tweets after the event, Jones said he declined to be interviewed at the event because he was there to support a local business, not endorse a political candidate.

value.title: Trump administration gives notice to Congress on three planned arms sales to Taiwan
value.excerpt: The Trump administration has alerted Congress of its intent to move forward with three advanced weapons sales to Taiwan, a congressional aide and a source familiar told CNN Monday.

value.title: Read: Kamala Harris' remarks at the Supreme Court confirmation hearing

value.title: Trump claims Nov. 3 'will be the most exciting day in US election history'
value.excerpt: President Trump on Monday said this Election Day will be “the most exciting” in U.S. history, touting the “tremendous excitement and enthusiasm” among the electorate, while mocking his Democratic rival Joe Biden, saying “nobody” shows up to his events.

value.title: Ross Douthat column: There will be no Trump coup
value.excerpt: Three weeks from now, we will reach an end to speculation about what Donald Trump will do if he faces political defeat, whether he will leave power like a normal president or attempt some wild resistance.

value.title: Trump 'has been a champion' for the Black community: Paris Dennard

value.title: White House Says Republicans Will ‘Come Along With’ What Trump Wants On Stimulus
